'''Old Tionese''' was used to refer to the [[Colonist|colonial]] backwaters [[Khuteb]] and [[Promencius Four]].<ref name="BTC" />

==Behind the scenes==
Old Tionese was mentioned in the [[2015]] novel ''[[Battlefront: Twilight Company]]'', written by [[Alexander Freed]].<ref name="BTC" />

